metadata.name: I Loved You, Wasn't That Enough
metadata.description:
Each Ai was crafted 1 by 1, using Visual Expression of Emotional Verbiage. During a period I was battling with Angels & Demons, I attempted to turn my Emotion into Art, this is the result. Find my Emotion in each image.

Genesis Collection.

We Will Find Our End Together. Stay With Me.
